    "Retinal images that had been scaled were in RGB color space.",
    "After that, grayscale versions of the RGB images are obtained.",
    "Additionally, this procedure is necessary because it enhances the image attributes that are important for subsequent processing while also improving the image data.",
    "For this reason, the grayscale channel is used to analyze the retinal images.",
    "Fourth Order PDE based FilterIt has been researched that scale-space analysis and image enhancement (noise removal) can both benefit from the application of second-order partial differential equations (PDE)."
